---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Imperial Picks" description="Read the Privacy Policy for Imperial Picks (https://imperialpicks.in). Learn how we collect, store, and protect your information, including cookies, analytics, and browser storage usage.">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="relative bg-slate-50 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Background Patterns -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <!-- Header Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-16 pb-10 sm:pt-20 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
          <span>Website URL: <a href="https://imperialpicks.in" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">https://imperialpicks.in</a></span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline text-slate-300">•</span>
          <span>Last Updated: June 10, 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Policy Content -->
    <section class="relative py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-xs space-y-8">
          
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              At Imperial Picks, we value and respect your privacy. This Privacy Policy details the types of information we collect, how we manage, store, and safeguard your data, and your compliance rights when you browse our catalog at <a href="https://imperialpicks.in" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">https://imperialpicks.in</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 1 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              1. Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We collect information in several ways to support your user experience and verify submission integrity:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              <li>
                <strong>Newsletter Subscriptions:</strong> When you subscribe to our digest, we collect your email address. This database is managed securely.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Contact Form Submissions:</strong> When you send a message or request a tool review, we collect your name, email address, and any text inputs.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Anonymized Traffic Logs:</strong> We collect aggregate metadata, such as browser version, screen dimensions, time of visit, and referring website URLs.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 2 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              2. Cookies & Local Storage
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Imperial Picks utilizes standard browser storage technologies to maintain platform features:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              <li>
                <strong>Cookies:</strong> Small text files containing session identifiers to analyze aggregate visitor traffic and manage cookie consent preferences.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Local Storage:</strong> We use local storage variables (e.g., <code>voted_[tool_id]</code>) directly on your device to keep track of products you upvote. This prevents automated click bots from inflating voting metrics and does not track personal data.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 3 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              3. Google Analytics
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We integrate Google Analytics to track visitor demographics, clicks, and pageviews anonymously. Google Analytics records your IP address to determine geographic traffic locations, but this data is aggregated and does not identify you individually. You can opt-out of tracking by adjusting cookie permissions or installing browser-level blocker extensions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 4 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              4. Third-Party Links & Networks
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Our website publishes reviews, summaries, and links directing you to external websites (AI models, SaaS software, developer resources). Once you exit Imperial Picks, we have no control over the cookies, tracking behaviors, or policies of those third-party sites. We encourage you to inspect the privacy guidelines of any platform you choose to join.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 5 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              5. GDPR & CCPA Compliance Rights
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Under modern privacy legislations (such as GDPR and CCPA), you possess specific rights regarding your personal information:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              <li>
                <strong>Right to Access:</strong> You can request a summary of any data we hold about you (such as your newsletter email).
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> You can request updates to inaccurate or incomplete records.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Right to Deletion:</strong> You can request that we remove your email from our system entirely.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Right to Opt-Out:</strong> You can unsubscribe from newsletter communications instantly by clicking the link at the footer of our emails.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 6 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              6. Data Security
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We apply industry-standard security protocols to keep our website secure (including active SSL encryption). However, no internet transmission is 100% secure. While we protect our database using strict access limits, we cannot guarantee total immunity from malicious intrusion.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Details -->
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-slate-900">Privacy Inquiries</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              For privacy-related questions, data removal requests, or clarifications, contact our data manager at:
              <a href="mailto:contact@imperialpicks.in" class="text-indigo-600 font-bold hover:underline ml-1">
                contact@imperialpicks.in
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
